{"id": 3770, "name": "Projet de loi de finances pour 2025, n\u00b0\u00a0324", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/0324A/AN/3770", "date": "2024-10-29", "status": "Adopt\u00e9", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "Claire", "last_name": "Marais-Beuil", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Christine", "last_name": "Loir", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Mich\u00e8le", "last_name": "Martinez", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Sandrine", "last_name": "Dogor-Such", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thierry", "last_name": "Frapp\u00e9", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Anthony", "last_name": "Boulogne", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Lisette", "last_name": "Pollet", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "B\u00e9atrice", "last_name": "Roullaud", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "S\u00e9bastien", "last_name": "Chenu", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thierry", "last_name": "Tesson", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "G\u00e9raldine", "last_name": "Grangier", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Caroline", "last_name": "Colombier", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Philippe", "last_name": "Lottiaux", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Laurence", "last_name": "Robert-Dehault", "party": "Rassemblement National"}], "summary": "L\u2019amendement N\u00b0I-2885 rappelle ces produits de vapotage sont r\u00e9glement\u00e9s en France mais non tax\u00e9s.\n\nToutefois, la cr\u00e9ation d\u2019une fiscalit\u00e9 aux produits de vapotage doit \u00eatre appliqu\u00e9 de mani\u00e8re \u00e9quitable.\n\nLes buralistes ne sont pas les seuls \u00e0 vendre ce type de produits, les sites en lignes qui vendent ces produits, et les boutiques de vapotages doivent \u00e9galement \u00eatre soumis \u00e0 cette taxation."}